title: FROM JULY 2021: Rosie! (Reupload)
itunes:title: FROM JULY 2021: Rosie! (Reupload)
description:
Danny re-releases his favorite interview of 2021, with Rosie O'Donnell! The initial airing was July, but in case you missed it, it's here again. Danny and Ro talked about her 90s talk show and so much more. Happy Holidays! Danny will be back in the new year with brand new episodes of Everything Iconic!
